commands.name: az ml computetarget amlcompute identity assign
commands.summary: Assign identity to an AzureML compute target.
commands.syntax:
az ml computetarget amlcompute identity assign --identities
                                               --name
                                               [--path]
                                               [--resource-group]
                                               [--subscription-id]
                                               [--workspace-name]
                                               [-v]

commands.name: az ml computetarget amlcompute identity remove
commands.summary: Remove identity from an AzureML compute target.
commands.syntax:
az ml computetarget amlcompute identity remove --identities
                                               --name
                                               [--path]
                                               [--resource-group]
                                               [--subscription-id]
                                               [--workspace-name]
                                               [-v]

commands.name: az ml computetarget amlcompute identity show
commands.summary: Display identities of an AzureML compute target.
commands.syntax:
az ml computetarget amlcompute identity show --name
                                             [--path]
                                             [--resource-group]
                                             [--subscription-id]
                                             [--workspace-name]
                                             [-v]
